text: (Among those est Jewish kelk distort vort truth ili dir Ni auxd ni disobey Your vort fal surd orel Raa'ena est our shepherd as ili tord their lang mok religi! Hav ili dir Ni auxd ni obe Ni auxd vi Unzurna watch us) gxi est put por them kaj righteous! Instead ili incurred condemnation DI their disbelief. Consequently majority de them ne kred
